<LP>
   ACTION INDUSTRIES Inc. (Pittsburgh) -- Sholom D. Comay,
vice chairman, was named chairman of this marketer of
housewares and giftware. Mr. Comay, 52 years old, succeeds
Ernest S. Berez, 64, who retires at the end of July. The vice
chairman post won't be filled.
